Here is a summary of the Gujarati couplet:

Dvij Narayana Ji is a noble person, and Gajoji is a great warrior; 
He is a devotee of God from childhood and has a community of devoted followers.

Here is a 1-2 line summarization of the Gujarati couplet:

Lord Krishna and King Naraayan Ji are revered as devotees; 
Similarly, God Tejo Ji and brother Jethi Bhayia are also devout followers.
